data.description: Unbeatable location! Spacious two-story townhome on a quiet cul-de-sac in Carlisle Cove literally has it all nearby. Easy access to I-90, Elgin-O'Hare expressway, or the Schaumburg Metra station. Plus: Woodfield shopping, restaurants, entertainment, parks, walking paths, and it's a stone's throw from the Meineke Recreation Center Park and Swimming Pool. This one features a roomy kitchen with lots of cabinets and extra counter space, a dining room with office space that opens to the kitchen, separate living room, generous bedrooms (the master has a nice walk-in closet), and a full basement (rare for this area) adds further storage options, flexibility, and expansion potential up to approx 2000sq/ft. Great semi-private yard space and patio too with plenty of room to grill and chill. Brand new water heater (12/2023). Home warranty included. Make it yours!
